caption:
NewYork-Presbyterian’s #NICU champions are game-day ready! 🏈

With a little help from our child life specialists, these tiny teammates suited up to cheer on the @chiefs and the @philadelphiaeagles ahead of the big game and celebrated with their families.

“It was adorable and fun seeing my boys dressed up,” said Aysha, mom to twins Kayden and Ayden, who were dressed as #Chiefs quarterback @PatrickMahomes and an #Eagles player. “Seeing Delilah celebrate her first Super Bowl has brought me so much joy,” said her mom Dakeema. “Even in the hospital, moments like this bring so much light. I am grateful to the NICU staff for making these memories possible!”

No matter which team you’re rooting for, we can all agree these little fighters are the true MVPs. 

Drop a comment to help us cheer them on! 👏
